{"title":"乡情（二首）","authors":["刘章"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":12,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡情（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农家夏夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚风射火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月似弓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小院茶桌上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有几杯星星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一家人轻摇蒲扇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象棕树一丛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇啊摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇个不停，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我的心儿扇到南宁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小院宽敞了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象农家的心胸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小院洁净了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象头上的天空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再也没有瓜架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投下满地阴影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（那些年，只有小院，可以自己耕种，恨不得把庄稼种上灶坑！）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说赏心乐事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对良宵夜景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有几盆花儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗香浮动……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老才哥的批评"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看望老才哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正欣赏门前垂柳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听他在屋内，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在批评侄女大妞："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱们山里人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可不兴这么保守。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学会照相了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就不再姓刘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哼！钻到小黑屋洗像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听说不让人瞅……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一进门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见姑娘笑得眼泪流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老才哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愣愣地挖着烟斗。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}